    <main class="about-section">
      <h1 class="about-title">About NewsHub</h1>
      <p class="about-intro">
        Welcome to <strong>NewsHub</strong> – your one-stop platform to stay
        informed with the latest global headlines. We pull breaking news from
        reliable sources and display them in a clean and accessible interface,
        making news reading a breeze.
      </p>

      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-card">
          <h2>📌 Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            To deliver fast, reliable, and unbiased news from around the world
            in a clutter-free interface. We believe in empowering readers with
            information.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <h2>⚙️ How It Works</h2>
          <p>
            NewsHub uses a public news API to fetch real-time articles across
            categories. The data is processed and displayed in a sleek React
            frontend or EJS-rendered view.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-card">
          <h2>💡 Built By</h2>
          <p>
            Developed by <strong>Mohammad Kaif</strong> – a passionate software
            developer exploring full-stack development with JavaScript, React,
            Node.js, and more.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>© 2025 NewsHub. Built with ❤️ by Kaif.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
